[{"id": 556542, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1708, "text": "Elif, Lam, Mim, Ra. Bunlar Kitab'\u0131n ayetleridir. Ve sana Rabbinden indirilen hakt\u0131r. Ancak insanlar\u0131n \u00e7o\u011fu iman etmezler."}, {"id": 556543, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1709, "text": "Allah O'dur ki, g\u00f6kleri dayanak olmaks\u0131z\u0131n y\u00fckseltti; onlar\u0131 g\u00f6rmektesiniz. Sonra ar\u015fa istiva etti ve g\u00fcne\u015f ile aya boyun e\u011fdirdi, her biri ad\u0131 konulmu\u015f bir s\u00fcreye kadar ak\u0131p gitmektedirler. Her i\u015fi evirip d\u00fczenler, ayetleri birer birer a\u00e7\u0131klar. Umulur ki, Rabbinize kavu\u015faca\u011f\u0131n\u0131za kesin bilgiyle inan\u0131rs\u0131n\u0131z."}, {"id": 556544, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1710, "text": "Ve O, yeri yay\u0131p uzatan, onda sars\u0131lmaz-da\u011flar ve \u0131rmaklar k\u0131land\u0131r. Orada \u00fcr\u00fcnlerin her birinden iki\u015fer \u00e7ift yaratm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r; geceyi g\u00fcnd\u00fcze b\u00fcr\u00fcmektedir. \u015e\u00fcphesiz bunlarda d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnen bir topluluk i\u00e7in ger\u00e7ekten ayetler vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 556545, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1711, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde birbirine yak\u0131n kom\u015fu k\u0131talar vard\u0131r; \u00fcz\u00fcm ba\u011flar\u0131, ekinler, \u00e7atall\u0131 ve \u00e7atals\u0131z hurmal\u0131klar da vard\u0131r ki, bunlar ayn\u0131 su ile sulan\u0131r; ama \u00fcr\u00fcnlerinde (ki verimde ve lezzette) baz\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 baz\u0131s\u0131na \u00fcst\u00fcn k\u0131l\u0131yoruz. \u015e\u00fcphesiz, bunlarda akl\u0131n\u0131 kullanan bir topluluk i\u00e7in ger\u00e7ekten ayetler vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 556546, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1712, "text": "E\u011fer \u015fa\u015f\u0131racaksan, as\u0131l \u015fa\u015fk\u0131nl\u0131k konusu onlar\u0131n \u015f\u00f6yle s\u00f6ylemeleridir: \"Biz toprak iken mi, ger\u00e7ekten biz mi yeniden yarat\u0131laca\u011f\u0131z?\" \u0130\u015fte onlar Rablerine kar\u015f\u0131 inkara sapanlar, i\u015fte onlar boyunlar\u0131na (ate\u015ften) halkalar ge\u00e7irilenler ve i\u015fte onlar -i\u00e7inde ebedi kalacaklar\u0131- ate\u015fin arkada\u015flar\u0131 olanlard\u0131r."}, {"id": 556547, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1713, "text": "Onlar, iyilikten \u00f6nce k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc \u00e7abukla\u015ft\u0131rmak istiyorlar; oysa onlardan \u00f6nce nice \u00f6rnekler gelip-ge\u00e7mi\u015ftir. Ve \u015f\u00fcphesiz, senin Rabbin, zul\u00fcmlerine kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k insanlar i\u00e7in ba\u011f\u0131\u015flama sahibidir ve \u015f\u00fcphesiz senin Rabbin, cezas\u0131 \u00e7ok \u015fiddetli oland\u0131r."}, {"id": 556548, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1714, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler derler ki: \"Ona Rabbinden bir ayet (mucize) indirilseydi ya.\" Sen, yaln\u0131zca bir uyar\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n ve her topluluk i\u00e7in bir hidayet \u00f6nderisin."}, {"id": 556549, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1715, "text": "Allah, her di\u015finin neyi y\u00fcklendi\u011fini (neye hamile kald\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131) ve d\u00f6l yataklar\u0131n\u0131n neyi eksiltip neyi ekledi\u011fini bilir. O'nun Kat\u0131nda her\u015fey bir miktar (\u00f6l\u00e7\u00fc) iledir."}, {"id": 556550, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1716, "text": "O, gayb\u0131 da, m\u00fc\u015fahede edileni de bilendir. Pek b\u00fcy\u00fckt\u00fcr, Y\u00fccedir."}, {"id": 556551, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1717, "text": "Sizden s\u00f6z\u00fc sakl\u0131 tutan da, onu a\u00e7\u0131\u011fa vuran da, geceleyin gizlenen de ve g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fcn ortakl\u0131kta gezen de (O'nun Kat\u0131nda bilme bak\u0131m\u0131ndan) birdir."}, {"id": 556552, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1718, "text": "O'nun (insan\u0131n) \u00f6n\u00fcnden ve arkas\u0131ndan izleyenleri vard\u0131r, onu Allah'\u0131n emriyle g\u00f6zetip-korumaktad\u0131rlar. Ger\u00e7ekten Allah, kendi nefis (\u00f6z)lerinde olan\u0131 de\u011fi\u015ftirip bozuncaya kadar, bir toplulukta olan\u0131 de\u011fi\u015ftirip-bozmaz. Allah bir toplulu\u011fa k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fck istedi mi, art\u0131k onu geri \u00e7evirmeye hi\u00e7bir (bi\u00e7imde imkan) yoktur; onlar i\u00e7in O'ndan ba\u015fka bir veli yoktur."}, {"id": 556553, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1719, "text": "O size \u015fim\u015fe\u011fi korku ve umut olarak g\u00f6steren, (ya\u011fmur y\u00fckl\u00fc) a\u011f\u0131rla\u015fm\u0131\u015f bulutlar\u0131 (in\u015fa edip) ortaya \u00e7\u0131karand\u0131r."}, {"id": 556554, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1720, "text": "G\u00f6k g\u00fcr\u00fclt\u00fcs\u00fc O'nu hamd ile, melekler de O'na olan korkular\u0131ndan tesbih ederler.. O, y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131mlar\u0131 g\u00f6nderip bununla diledi\u011fine \u00e7arpar; onlar ise Allah hakk\u0131nda \u00e7eki\u015fip-tart\u0131\u015f\u0131rlar. O, g\u00fcc\u00fc (ve cezas\u0131) pek \u00e7etin oland\u0131r."}, {"id": 556555, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1721, "text": "Hak olan \u00e7a\u011fr\u0131 (dua, ibadet) yaln\u0131zca O'na (olan)d\u0131r. Onlar\u0131n Allah'tan ba\u015fka \u00e7a\u011f\u0131rd\u0131klar\u0131 ise, onlara hi\u00e7bir \u015feyle cevab veremezler. (Onlar\u0131n durumu) yaln\u0131zca, a\u011fz\u0131na gelsin diye, iki avucunu suya uzatan(\u0131n bo\u015funa beklemesi) gibidir. Oysa ona gelmez. \u0130nkar edenlerin duas\u0131, sap\u0131kl\u0131k i\u00e7inde olmaktan ba\u015fkas\u0131 de\u011fildir."}, {"id": 556556, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": true, "sajda_id": 2, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": true, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1722, "text": "G\u00f6klerde ve yerde her ne varsa -isteyerek de olsa, istemeyerek de olsa- Allah'a secde eder. Sabah ak\u015fam g\u00f6lgeleri de (O'na secde eder)."}, {"id": 556557, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1723, "text": "De ki: \"G\u00f6klerin ve yerin Rabbi kimdir?\" De ki: \"Allah't\u0131r.\" De ki: \"\u00d6yleyse, O'nu b\u0131rak\u0131p kendilerine bile yarar da, zarar da sa\u011flamaya g\u00fc\u00e7 yetiremeyen birtak\u0131m veliler mi (tanr\u0131lar) edindiniz?\" De ki: \"Hi\u00e7 g\u00f6rmeyen (a'ma) ile g\u00f6ren (basiret sahibi) e\u015fit olabilir mi? Veya karanl\u0131klarla nur e\u015fit olabilir mi?\" Yoksa Allah'a, O'nun yaratmas\u0131 gibi yaratan ortaklar buldular da, bu yaratma, kendilerince birbirine mi benze\u015fti? De ki: \"Allah, her\u015feyin Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131'd\u0131r ve O, tektir, kahredici oland\u0131r.\""}, {"id": 556559, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1724, "text": "(Allah) G\u00f6kten bir su indirdi de dereler kendi miktar\u0131nca \u00e7a\u011flay\u0131p akt\u0131. Sel de y\u00fcze vuran bir k\u00f6p\u00fck y\u00fcklendi. Bir s\u00fcs veya bir meta sa\u011flamak i\u00e7in ate\u015fte \u00fczerine yak\u0131p-erittikleri \u015feyler (madenler)de de bunun gibi bir k\u00f6p\u00fck (art\u0131k) vard\u0131r. \u0130\u015fte Allah, hak ile bat\u0131la b\u00f6yle \u00f6rnekler verir. K\u00f6p\u00fc\u011fe gelince, o at\u0131l\u0131r gider, insanlara yarar sa\u011flayacak \u015fey ise, yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde kal\u0131r. \u0130\u015fte Allah \u00f6rnekleri b\u00f6yle vermektedir."}, {"id": 556560, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1725, "text": "Rablerine icabet edenlere daha g\u00fczeli vard\u0131r. O'na icabet etmeyenler ise, yery\u00fcz\u00fcndekilerin t\u00fcm\u00fc ve bununla birlikte bir kat\u0131 daha onlar\u0131n olsa mutlaka (kurtulmak i\u00e7in) bunu fidye olarak verirlerdi. Sorgulaman\u0131n en k\u00f6t\u00fcs\u00fc onlar i\u00e7indir. Onlar\u0131n bar\u0131nma yerleri cehennemdir, ne k\u00f6t\u00fc bir yarat\u0131kt\u0131r o!.."}, {"id": 556561, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1726, "text": "Peki, sana Rabbinden indirilenin ger\u00e7ekten hak oldu\u011funu bilen ki\u015fi, o g\u00f6rmeyen (a'ma) gibi midir? Ancak temiz ak\u0131l sahipleri \u00f6\u011f\u00fct al\u0131p-d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnebilirler."}, {"id": 556562, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1727, "text": "Onlar Allah'\u0131n ahdini yerine getirirler ve verdikleri kesin s\u00f6z\u00fc (misak\u0131) bozmazlar."}, {"id": 556563, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1728, "text": "Ve onlar Allah'\u0131n ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 emretti\u011fi \u015feyi ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131rlar. Rablerinden i\u00e7leri sayg\u0131 ile titrer, k\u00f6t\u00fc hesaptan korkarlar."}, {"id": 556564, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1729, "text": "Ve onlar-Rablerinin y\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc (ho\u015fnutlu\u011funu) isteyerek sabrederler, namaz\u0131 dosdo\u011fru k\u0131larlar, kendilerine r\u0131z\u0131k olarak verdiklerimizden gizli ve a\u00e7\u0131k infak ederler ve k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc iyilikle savarlar. \u0130\u015fte onlar, bu yurdun (d\u00fcnyan\u0131n g\u00fczel) sonucu (ahiret mutlulu\u011fu) onlar i\u00e7indir."}, {"id": 556565, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1730, "text": "Onlar, Adn cennetlerine girerler. Babalar\u0131ndan, e\u015flerinden ve soylar\u0131ndan 'salih davran\u0131\u015flarda' bulunanlar da (Adn cennetlerine girer). Melekler onlara her bir kap\u0131dan girip (\u015f\u00f6yle derler:)"}, {"id": 556566, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1731, "text": "\"Sabretti\u011finize kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k selam size. (D\u00fcnya) Yurdun(un) sonu ne g\u00fczel.\""}, {"id": 556567, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1732, "text": "Allah'a verdikleri s\u00f6z\u00fc, onu kesin olarak onaylad\u0131ktan sonra bozanlar, Allah'\u0131n ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 emretti\u011fi \u015feyi kesip-koparanlar ve yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bozgunculuk \u00e7\u0131karanlar; i\u015fte onlar, lanet onlar i\u00e7indir ve yurdun k\u00f6t\u00fc olan\u0131 da onlar i\u00e7indir."}, {"id": 556568, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1733, "text": "Allah diledi\u011fine r\u0131zk\u0131 geni\u015fletir-yayar ve daralt\u0131r da. Onlar ise d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131na sevindiler. Oysaki d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131, ahirette (ki s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z mutluluk yan\u0131nda ge\u00e7ici) bir meta'dan ba\u015fkas\u0131 de\u011fildir."}, {"id": 556570, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1734, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler: \"Ona Rabbinden bir ayet (mucize) indirilseydi ya!\" derler. De ki: \"\u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, diledi\u011fini \u015fa\u015f\u0131rt\u0131p-sapt\u0131r\u0131r, Kendisi'ne kat\u0131ks\u0131zca y\u00f6neleni de dosdo\u011fru yola y\u00f6neltip-iletir.\""}, {"id": 556571, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1735, "text": "Bunlar, iman edenler ve kalpleri Allah'\u0131n zikriyle mutmain olanlard\u0131r. Haberiniz olsun; kalpler yaln\u0131zca Allah'\u0131n zikriyle mutmain olur."}, {"id": 556572, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1736, "text": "\u0130man edip salih amellerde bulunanlar, ne mutlu onlara. Var\u0131lacak yerin g\u00fczel olan\u0131 (onlar\u0131nd\u0131r)."}, {"id": 556573, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1737, "text": "B\u00f6ylece Biz seni, kendisinden \u00f6nce nice \u00fcmmetler gelip-ge\u00e7mi\u015f olan bir \u00fcmmete (el\u00e7i olarak) g\u00f6nderdik; sana vahyettiklerimizi onlara okuyas\u0131n diye. Oysa onlar Rahman'a nank\u00f6rl\u00fck ediyorlar. De ki: \"O, benim Rabbimdir, O'ndan ba\u015fka \u0130lah yoktur. Ben O'na tevekk\u00fcl ettim ve son d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f O'nad\u0131r.\""}, {"id": 556574, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1738, "text": "E\u011fer kendisiyle da\u011flar\u0131n y\u00fcr\u00fct\u00fcld\u00fc\u011f\u00fc, yerin par\u00e7aland\u0131\u011f\u0131 veya \u00f6l\u00fclerin konu\u015fturuldu\u011fu bir Kur'an olsayd\u0131 (yine bu Kur'an olurdu). Hay\u0131r, emrin t\u00fcm\u00fc Allah'\u0131nd\u0131r. \u0130man edenler hala anlamad\u0131lar m\u0131 ki, e\u011fer Allah dilemi\u015f olsayd\u0131, insanlar\u0131n t\u00fcm\u00fcn\u00fc hidayete erdirmi\u015f olurdu. \u0130nkar edenler, Allah'\u0131n va\u2019di gelinceye kadar, yapt\u0131klar\u0131 dolay\u0131s\u0131yla ya ba\u015flar\u0131na \u00e7etin bir bela \u00e7atacak veya yurtlar\u0131n\u0131n yak\u0131n\u0131na inecek. \u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, verdi\u011fi s\u00f6zden d\u00f6nmez. (Veya miad\u0131n\u0131 \u015fa\u015f\u0131rmaz.)"}, {"id": 556575, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1739, "text": "Andolsun, senden \u00f6nceki el\u00e7ilerle de alay edildi, bunun \u00fczerine Ben de o inkara sapanlara bir s\u00fcre tan\u0131d\u0131m, sonra onlar\u0131 (k\u0131sk\u0131vrak) yakalay\u0131verdim. \u0130\u015fte nas\u0131ld\u0131 sonu\u00e7land\u0131rma?"}, {"id": 556576, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1740, "text": "Her nefsin b\u00fct\u00fcn kazand\u0131klar\u0131 \u00fczerinde g\u00f6zetici olana m\u0131 (ba\u015f kald\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r?) Onlar Allah'a ortaklar ko\u015ftular. De ki: \"Bunlar\u0131 adland\u0131r\u0131n (bakal\u0131m). Yoksa siz yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bilmeyece\u011fi bir \u015feyi O'na haber mi veriyorsunuz? Yoksa s\u00f6z\u00fcn zahirine (veya bo\u015f ve s\u00fcsl\u00fc olan\u0131na)mi (kan\u0131yorsunuz)? Hay\u0131r, inkar edenlere kendi hileli-d\u00fczenleri s\u00fcsl\u00fc-\u00e7ekici g\u00f6sterilmi\u015ftir ve onlar (do\u011fru) yoldan al\u0131konulmu\u015flard\u0131r. Allah, kimi sapt\u0131r\u0131rsa, art\u0131k onun i\u00e7in hi\u00e7bir yol g\u00f6sterici yoktur."}, {"id": 556577, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1741, "text": "D\u00fcnya hayat\u0131nda onlar i\u00e7in bir azap vard\u0131r, ahiretin azab\u0131 ise daha zorludur. Onlar\u0131 Allah'tan (kurtaracak) hi\u00e7bir koruyucu da yoktur."}, {"id": 556579, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1742, "text": "Takva sahiplerine vadedilen cennet; onun alt\u0131ndan \u0131rmaklar akar, yemi\u015fleri ve g\u00f6lgelikleri s\u00fcreklidir. Bu korkup-sak\u0131nanlar\u0131n (mutlu) sonudur, inkar edenlerin sonu ise ate\u015ftir."}, {"id": 556580, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1743, "text": "Kendilerine kitap verdiklerimiz, sana indirilen dolay\u0131s\u0131yla sevinirler; fakat (M\u00fcsl\u00fcmanlar\u0131n aleyhinde birle\u015fen) gruplardan, onun baz\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 inkar edenler vard\u0131r. De ki: \"Ben, yaln\u0131zca Allah'a kulluk etmek ve O'na ortak ko\u015fmamakla emrolundum. Ben ancak O'na davet ederim ve son d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f\u00fcm O'nad\u0131r.\""}, {"id": 556581, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1744, "text": "\u0130\u015fte b\u00f6ylece Biz onu (Kur'an'\u0131) Arap\u00e7a bir h\u00fck\u00fcm olarak indirdik. Andolsun, sana gelen bu ilimden sonra, onlar\u0131n heva (istek ve tutku)lar\u0131na uyacak olursan, senin i\u00e7in Allah'tan ne bir yard\u0131mc\u0131, dost, ne bir koruyucu vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 556582, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1745, "text": "Andolsun, senden \u00f6nce de el\u00e7iler g\u00f6nderdik, onlara e\u015fler ve \u00e7ocuklar verdik. Allah'\u0131n izni olmaks\u0131z\u0131n (hi\u00e7)bir el\u00e7iye herhangi bir ayeti (mucizeyi) getirmek olacak i\u015f de\u011fildi. Her ecel (tespit edilmi\u015f s\u00fcre) i\u00e7in bir kitap (yaz\u0131, h\u00fck\u00fcm, son) vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 556583, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1746, "text": "Allah, diledi\u011fini ortadan kald\u0131r\u0131r ve b\u0131rak\u0131r. Kitab\u0131n anas\u0131 O'nun Kat\u0131ndad\u0131r."}, {"id": 556584, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1747, "text": "Onlara (azap olarak) va'dettiklerimizden bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 sana g\u00f6stersek de, senin hayat\u0131na son versek de, sana d\u00fc\u015fen yaln\u0131zca tebli\u011fdir ve hesap da Bize aittir."}, {"id": 556585, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1748, "text": "Onlar g\u00f6rm\u00fcyorlar m\u0131 ki, ger\u00e7ekten Biz arza geliyor ve onu \u00e7evresinden eksiltiyoruz. Allah h\u00fck\u00fcm verir. O'nun h\u00fckm\u00fcn\u00fcn pe\u015fine d\u00fc\u015fecek yoktur. Ve O, hesab\u0131 pek \u00e7abuk g\u00f6rendir."}, {"id": 556586, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1749, "text": "Onlardan \u00f6ncekiler de hileli-d\u00fczenler kurmu\u015flard\u0131; fakat d\u00fczen kuruculu\u011fun (tedbirlerin, kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k vermelerin) t\u00fcm\u00fc Allah'a aittir. Her bir nefsin ne kazand\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 O bilir. Bu yurdun sonu kimindir, inkar edenler pek yak\u0131nda bileceklerdir."}, {"id": 556587, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 255, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1750, "text": "O inkar edenler \u015f\u00f6yle derler: \"Sen g\u00f6nderilmi\u015f (Allah'\u0131n bir el\u00e7isi) de\u011filsin.\" De ki: \"Benimle sizin aran\u0131zda \u015fahid olarak Allah yeter ve yanlar\u0131nda kitab\u0131n ilmi bulunanlar da (bu ger\u00e7e\u011fi bilir).\""}]